Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no cards left in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your mind has now been sealed within this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! I'll defeat you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final tournament shall begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this very Duel Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of the four remaining Duelists shall earn the right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to challenge me for eternal fame and glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy... Even if you wield the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is all but ineffective before my Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,108)}The Night Before the Finals!\NPegasus' Secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo-hoo! {\i1}Delicious{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The best I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourselves and prepare for the tournament tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help yourselves. We have prepared you all a very special meal in celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I have something I must address with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will all be required to have one of these cards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you received in your invitation during the final tournament tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is "Glory of the King's Right", and the second is "Glory of the King's Left".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cards...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones holding Glory to the King's Right can seize the grand cash prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those wielding Glory to the King's Left may challenge Master Pegasus directly for his title.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course I don't have that after barging in the way I did...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What'da I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look down at the soup we have prepared for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole! Ya think we're gonna eat this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look inside them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now begin selecting the tournament matchups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's going to face who...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter who I face, I'm going to {\b0}win{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\i1}Anyone{\b1} but Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's got C?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask for a better opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might wanna back outta this while ya still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you, Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm not holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I'll fight my hardest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results have been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match will be Master Yugi Mutou versus Lady Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Followed by Master Bandit Keith versus Master Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we sincerely hope you enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't eat another bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you still ate that after finding an eye in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to win Pegasus' tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have the card...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we came to this island, we split our Star Chips in half, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Glory to the King's Right card belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can use the prize money for Shizuka-chan's eye operation, alright Jounouchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll hold onto this card, Glory to the King's Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get Grandpa back, I've got to beat Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take it with deep gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for me to head off on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'm looking forward to our Duel tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight then-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, let's get those honors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you'd better win!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa... Kaiba-kun... And Mokuba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to save you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... It's finally time for us to settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun, let's just let it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come {\i1}on{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? You think Kaiba-kun lost because he {\i1}cheated{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If you think about all the times Pegasus messed with us up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a high possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to find out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}is{\i0} our enemy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't surprise me if he's tweaked the situation to his advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, Yugi and the others were bound to lose from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Anzu, you gonna allow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that {\i1}is{\i0} true, of course I won't stand for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? So let's go find the proof we need to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should fight this match fair-and-square!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be bad if we get caught while searching for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't bother Yugi and Jounouchi the night before the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta do this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be of some use!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}can't{\i0} be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Grandpa's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! I'm this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! Please save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a spy camera or something around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's {\i1}nothing here{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Pegasus honestly beat Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I highly doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm forced into trials I'm bound to lose, I always become cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This light...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming in from the opening up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda, can you stand on that platform?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand there just like Kaiba-kun was!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bingo alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very possible that he had someone holding a camera, viewing the Duel Ring from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, it'd be easy for someone to spy from the window there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they can reveal the enemy's cards to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about as cunning as you can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with a camera view of that, he'd be able to completely reveal the opponent's strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a secret room in that tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, let's head over to that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eh{\i0}?! We're going {\i1}that{\i0} far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's painful...! Hurry up and save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already! I told you to leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hope to beat Yugi, I must think up a new set of strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's no way he's flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got to have a weak point {\b0}somewhere{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! Where are you?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... I've missed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hurts...! Hurry and get me out of here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! But {\i1}how{\i0}...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Try pulling me up {\i1}before{\i0} covering my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, let's {\i1}let it go{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, how do I save you from here? I don't know how!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save me! I'm in great pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}how{\i0} do I do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun... And Mokuba-kun as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get me out of here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save me, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Anzu, you climb up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, one of us can catch you if you slip by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! You don't {\i1}get{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious the {\i1}men{\i0} should go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't climb unless someone's here to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's painful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...! Save me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! Kaiba-kun! Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... That Pegasus man is a much more terrifying person than you realize...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared! Just {\i1}climb{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if she {\i1}does{\i0} fall, we can't save her like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Just freaking {\i1}climb{\i0}, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun, don't push me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Then just climb already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That man's heart has been engulfed in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's already gone to the Dark World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark World...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That man lives in the sorrowful darkness, only thinking about gaining the power he needs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll be fighting against that great darkness itself starting right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that Dark Power is stealing away my life this very moment...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! YUGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was terrible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't waste our time out here. We've gotta hurry up and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! There's nothing up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like some kind of painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really pretty, but I wonder who she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing's in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's related to Pegasus somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got busted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you guys have seen right through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that'll make this go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! We know you've been cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use trying to cover it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for me to cover anything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is because I am about to drag you three into another world entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to show you all the world I refer to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa! Kaiba-kun! Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point just sitting here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-kun, let's turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-You saw?\N-Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That you'll surely save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}YUGI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GRANDPA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Game?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:18:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient ritual played long ago where one's very being is put to the test... the {\i1}ultimate{\i0} game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those chosen are able to see it... within the Dark World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's he doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is his eye somehow related to this "Dark Game" he's spoken of...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've all taken an interest in this eye of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he just read our minds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He {\i1}couldn't{\i0} have..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Eye's power allows me to read other's minds using the Mind Scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I hold this power, I am untouchable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dark Power given to only the chosen ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to read {\i1}your{\i0} mind as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be, you are...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm certain I saw a Dark Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it... the Millennium Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with this, you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This idiot...! He's got such a damn loud voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this... With this I can beat Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really looking forward to tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That wasn't an ordinary dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain Grandpa was sending me a message!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-kun! Mokuba-kun! And Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what happens, I {\b0}will{\b1} save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,132)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The finals have finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's first opponent is the Mai Kujaku we know so well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no problem with Mai-san, but this Duel is going to Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong with you, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not stopping any of Mai-san's attacks...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you at all, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just calm down and focus on the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "Driven to Temptation! The Shadow of Temptation"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
